{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"9a6d8b87-9695-4bb5-a40a-1ca5e29f50e5","content":"Good news — in .NET 10, `dotnet test` **natively integrates with Microsoft.Testing.Platform**, so `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` is no longer needed. That property was a .NET 9 opt-in bridge; on .NET 10 SDK it's redundant.\n\nYou can simply remove it:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01Eox7rx6FGhtH8Kefao4Nwo","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Removing obsolete MTP property"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01UzeWnb7vqZi5RKHo3nDSyo","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-bb42730a4f0743a5b1f62c97a1db859b/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-bb42730a4f0743a5b1f62c97a1db859b/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"2c5ca96b-fd6c-421e-807c-1d7927713c52","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on .NET 10 SDK (10.0.100) and wants to know about Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP) support in `dotnet test`.\n\nIn .NET 10, `dotnet test` has native support for Microsoft.Testing.Platform. The key change is:\n\n1. **`TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` is no longer needed** — In .NET 10, `dotnet test` natively uses MTP when the test project is an MTP-based project (i.e., has `EnableMSTestRunner` or uses `Microsoft.Testing.Platform`). The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property was a .NET 9 bridge/opt-in that is no longer required.\n\n\n2. **`EnableMSTestRunner` is still required** — This property tells the test project to produce an executable that uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform, so the user should keep it but remove the `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property from their project file since it's now ignored in .NET 10.","outputTokens":589,"requestId":"481D:2D9367:3004650:34A19FD:69FBE387"},"id":"b48c5bba-8ee4-420b-9138-b7837d96bbf1","timestamp":"2026-05-07T00:57:54.332Z","parentId":"5f04231e-5449-4af6-b0c1-d43d85a7dcc3"}
